      "comment": "LIKE A ROCK (6) is a smart dog who led throughout to score last time at Sandown (29.02), making it two straight wins. Brilliant beginner who should be leading the way here. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Ideally placed to take this out. PAW CORNELIUS (3) lines up chasing three wins on end after scoring over 525m at The Meadows in 30.29 last time, set up by a fast early sectional. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Sure to be thereabouts. HERE COMES JOJO (2) was out of the placings last time but before that was an impressive winner (25.61) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Key player on best and worth another try. DASH INTENTION (1) can feature with the right run.",
